## Summary


shadcn/ui is your primary UI component library. It provides:
- ✅ Beautiful, accessible components out of the box
- ✅ Full control and customization (you own the code)
- ✅ Excellent TypeScript support
- ✅ Perfect integration with Tailwind CSS v4
- ✅ Built-in dark mode support
- ✅ Comprehensive documentation


Always use shadcn/ui components for UI elements before creating custom components or using other libraries. If a component doesn't exist, compose it from existing shadcn/ui primitives or request it be added via the CLI.




